PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?label WHERE {
  ?item wdt:P279 wd:Q3918 .
  ?item rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = "de" ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?label ) , "linguistik" ) )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?stadium ?stadiumLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q213417 wdt:P115 ?stadium .
  ?stadium rdfs:label ?stadiumLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?stadiumLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?countryLabel ( COUNT( ?winner ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?winner wdt:P166 ?award .
  ?award wdt:P31 / wdt:P279 * wd:Q123737 .
  ?winner wdt:P27 ?country .
  ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = "en" )
}
GROUP BY ?countryLabel
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )
LIMIT 1
OFFSET 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q9545 wdt:P2048 ?blairHeight .
  wd:Q10993 wdt:P2048 ?woodsHeight .
  BIND( STRBEFORE( ?blairHeight , " " ) AS ?blairNum ) BIND( STRBEFORE( ?woodsHeight , " " ) AS ?woodsNum ) FILTER ( xsd:decimal ( ?blairNum ) > xsd:decimal ( ?woodsNum ) )
}
